PDL-GSL-Randist

Comprehensive Perl Data Language (PDL) binding to the GNU Scientific Library
(GSL) Random Distribution (randist) functions.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

    perldoc PDL::GSL::Randist

